---
title: Sizzling Chinese Beef & Veggie Ramen Noodle Stir-Fry with Crushed Peanuts
description: For a dish that’s ready in a flash, you can’t beat this speedy bowl of sizzling Chinese beef, with delectable veggies, ramen noodles and peanuts for that perfect crunch. It’s ready in under half an hour too, so you can skip straight to the best part of cooking: the eating!
